.value.resource_description: Congratulations! You've got a free textbook. Download this guide to learn how to use it.
The Student Answer Guide contains answers to a subset of the problems and exercises in the text.
This resource provides the answers to the Be Prepared questions that begin each section of the textbook.

Click below to download the previous version of the Intermediate Algebra PDF. This version was used beginning in June 2017. The only difference between this version and the one available under “Get the book” in the Book Details tab is the numbering of Tables. The version under “Get this book” corrects an issue with table numbering.
Adapted from OpenStax College Success, this guide discusses effective reading approaches, study tips, and notetaking strategies for students.
Adapted from OpenStax College Success, this guide includes information about estimating time on tasks, avoiding procrastination, and using strategies to stick to your priorities.
